T1  - PERSISTENT IDEOLOGY AND THE DETERMINATION OF PUBLIC POLICY OVER TIME*
AU  - Song, Zheng
Y1  - 2012/02/01
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/02/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2011.00676.x
T2  - International Economic Review
